[package]
name = "linkcheck"
version = "0.4.1"
authors = [ "Michael-F-Bryan <michaelfbryan@gmail.com>",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
edition = "2018"
repository = "https://github.com/Michael-F-Bryan/linkcheck"
readme = "README.md"
description = "A library for extracting and validating links."
keywords = [ "linkchecker", "linkcheck", "links", "check",]
categories = [ "text-processing",]

[dependencies]
codespan = "0.11.0"
linkify = "0.7.0"
pulldown-cmark = "0.8"
reqwest = "0.11.1"
futures = "0.3.4"
log = "0.4.8"
thiserror = "1.0.15"
http = "0.2.1"
bytes = "1.0"
url = "2"
dunce = "1.0.0"
html5ever = "0.26.0"
markup5ever_rcdom = "0.2.0"
regex = "*"
lazy_static = "*"
mdbook = "0.4.21"

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "3.1.0"
pretty_assertions = "1"
env_logger = "0.9"

[features]
default = [ "serde-1",]
serde-1 = [ "serde", "url/serde", "codespan/serialization",]

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-developed"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
optional = true
features = [ "derive",]

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = [ "macros", "rt-multi-thread",]

[package]
name = "percent-encoding-iri"
version = "2.2.0"
authors = [ "The rust-url developers",]
description = "Percent encoding and decoding, preserving non-Latin characters."
categories = [ "no_std",]
repository = "https://github.com/servo/rust-url/"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
edition = "2018"
rust-version = "1.51"

[features]
default = [ "std",]
std = [ "alloc",]
alloc = []

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/ankitects/linkcheck"]
git = "https://github.com/ankitects/linkcheck"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "184b2ca50ed39ca43da13f0b830a463861adb9ca"

[source."https://github.com/ankitects/rust-url"]
git = "https://github.com/ankitects/rust-url"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "bb930b8d089f4d30d7d19c12e54e66191de47b88"
